<title>GREECE: DIARY OF ATHENS BOURSE RIGHTS ISSUES.</title>
<headline>DIARY OF ATHENS BOURSE RIGHTS ISSUES.</headline>
<dateline>ATHENS 1997-08-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>The following rights issues are</p>
<p>being made by companies listed on the Athens bourse.</p>
<p>The table is updated as new rights issues are approved by</p>
<p>the Athens stock exchange.</p>
<p>    SHARE		TERMS	  ISSUE	SUBSCRIPTION</p>
<p>					    PRICE	   PERIOD/</p>
<p>				     (in drachmas)     PROCEEDS</p>
