<p>					   Proceeds: 6.46 bln</p>
<p>Volos Technical     1-for-2	 1,100     July 21-August 28</p>
<p>					   Proceeds: 3.04 bln</p>
<p>Arcadia-Rokas	 2-for-10	1,900(c)  July 21-August 29</p>
<p>			     1,600(p)  Proceeds: 2.02 bln</p>
<p>Elval		   1-for-20	2,200     July 21-September 5</p>
<p>					    Proceeds: 3.04 bln</p>
<p>Themeliodomi	  3-for-10	2,050     August 1-September 3</p>
<p>					   Proceeds: 3.17 bln</p>
